Class ClaimList

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.CMPUT301W15T06.AppModel
      • ca.ualberta.CMPUT301W15T06.ClaimList

  • public class ClaimList
extends AppModel
    The ClaimList class is an sub-class of AppModel. This class can set up a ArrayList named ClaimList which contains Claim. The ClaimList can also be pushed online and pulled online, sort and search Claim. This class is associated with Claim for Claim information, Tag and TagList for searching by Tag names.
